    <item>
      <title>美国睡眠呼吸暂停问题得到解决后，飞利浦销量创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/philips-settles-sleep-apnea-claims-in-the-us-for-1-1-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国对睡眠呼吸暂停设备故障索赔的和解结果低于预期后，皇家飞利浦公司股价飙升创纪录水平，这引发了人们对这家制造商已经摆脱过去三年来困扰其的担忧的希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/philips-settles-sleep-apnea-claims-in-the-us-for-1-1-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 05:10:19 GMT</pubDate>
